headline: Trane Technologies Provides $1.5 Million Grant to Science Museum of Minnesota to Empower Youth Through STEM Programs
summary: SWORDS, IE / ACCESS Newswire / December 18, 2025 / Trane Technologies (NYSE:TT), a global climate innovator, proudly announces the renewal of its grant to the Science Museum of Minnesota, supporting the Kitty Andersen Youth Science Center (KAYSC). ...
